          <title>Course Description</title>

          <p>
            An introduction to algebraic structures including groups, rings, and fields, and their sub-structures, as well as homomorphisms and isomorphisms.
            Fundamental number theoretic topics are included to establish connections and provide examples in the context of abstract algebra.
         </p>
